OL,5, Links between Boris Johnson and BBC    
OL,6, chairman Richard Sharp are under fresh 
OL,7, scrutiny, following a report that the  
OL,8, then-prime minister was told to stop   
OL,9, asking Mr Sharp for financial advice.  
OL,11,FMr Sharp's appointment is under review 
OL,12,Ffollowing claims he helped Mr Johnson  
OL,13,Fsecure a loan before getting his job.  
OL,15,FBoth men have denied the claims.       
OL,17,FA leaked memo from Cabinet Secretary   
OL,18,FSimon Case, reported by the Sunday     
OL,19,FTimes, allegedly warns Mr Johnson to   
OL,20,F"no longer" ask for his advice.        
